    "sourcePath": "/Users/tobias.winkler/Downloads/compass_artifact_wf-b33581ad-754a-4a5a-b05f-ef15056377e0_text_markdown.md",
    "markdown": "### 17. MiniMax (China) — LLM ✓ TTS ✓ STT ✗\n\n**Status:** Active. **Industry-leading TTS quality** (#2 on Speech Arena).\n\n**LLM:** `minimax-m2.5` ($0.30/$1.20, 1M context), `minimax-m2.7` (new). OpenAI-compatible on third-party platforms.\n\n**TTS:** `speech-2.6-hd` ($130/1M chars, highest quality), `speech-2.6-turbo` ($78/1M chars, sub-250ms latency). **40+ languages.** Voice cloning (10s audio, $3/voice). Emotion control. Also available on Together AI, Replicate, Novita AI at lower prices.\n\nExcellent international access via platform.minimax.io. No Chinese phone required.",
